Run?

1229
01:46:20,076 --> 01:46:21,976
Get the horses out, quick

1230
01:46:23,146 --> 01:46:24,113
Hurry up

1231
01:46:24,580 --> 01:46:26,912
Kill all those who run

1232
01:46:34,190 --> 01:46:35,157
Go

