1266
01:49:38,608 --> 01:49:41,475
but he had escaped

1267
01:49:56,225 --> 01:49:58,250
Ge Li...

1268
01:49:58,661 --> 01:50:00,993
Ge Li...

1269
01:50:01,797 --> 01:50:03,662
