1281
01:50:44,707 --> 01:50:46,299
If this can really stop the war

1282
01:50:48,577 --> 01:50:50,568
and save more lives

1283
01:50:51,213 --> 01:50:52,544
why not?

1284
01:50:53,716 --> 01:50:54,774
...is it worth it?

1285
01:50:58,788 --> 01:51:01,450
