1286
01:51:01,490 --> 01:51:03,014
Go, quick

1287
01:51:04,160 --> 01:51:05,923
Keep moving, hurry up

1288
01:51:14,570 --> 01:51:17,835
Commander, I think Ge Li will not come

1289
