1292
01:51:33,622 --> 01:51:35,590
and protect our homeland

1293
01:51:36,592 --> 01:51:38,583
Isn't that just another battle field?

1294
01:51:38,627 --> 01:51:41,755
There's only victory & defeat

1295
01:51:43,165 --> 01:51:45,531
