1297
01:51:47,870 --> 01:51:50,202
Ge Li had lost

1298
01:51:50,239 --> 01:51:54,938
His theory is impractical,
idealism leads to jealousy

1299
01:51:55,978 --> 01:51:58,105
He can't even gain the trust

1300
01:51:58,147 --> 01:52:00,411
